*	the syntax-checker
*
*	to test this checker with oasys try:
*
*	#oasys
*	>f Checker.impl
*	Checker.impl>e checktest("fac")
*
*	Where fac ist the basename of a sourcefile ending with .mo (in this example: fac.mo)
